                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000103500b-b4f9-4d67-a23a-f2772721ecba" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(k=\frac{mg}{{X}_{1}}=\frac{1\times 9.8}{0.1}=98N{m}^{-1}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010103500b-b4f9-4d67-a23a-f2772721ecba">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000103500b-b4f9-4d67-a23a-f2772721ecba {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010103500b-b4f9-4d67-a23a-f2772721ecba {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000004083f08-651c-4844-8ccf-36da35f43191" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000104083f08-651c-4844-8ccf-36da35f43191">w&#216;Zxq †&#255;‡&#206;, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{1}{2}{kx}_{2}^{2}={m}^{{'}}g\left(h+{x}_{2}\right)⇒{x}_{2}^{2}={x}_{2}+1⇒{x}_{2}=1.618\ m\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000104083f08-651c-4844-8ccf-36da35f43191"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000004083f08-651c-4844-8ccf-36da35f43191 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000104083f08-651c-4844-8ccf-36da35f43191 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
