                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000001cc9e4ef-48ae-415c-8ac5-192463824a79" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({T}^{{'}}=2π\sqrt{\frac{L}{{g}^{{'}}}}=2π\sqrt{\frac{L}{\frac{4}{3}g}}\ =\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\times 2π\sqrt{\frac{L}{g}}=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}T\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011cc9e4ef-48ae-415c-8ac5-192463824a79"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001cc9e4ef-48ae-415c-8ac5-192463824a79 {margin-left: 0.35in;text-indent: -0.35in;text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000011cc9e4ef-48ae-415c-8ac5-192463824a79 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000e8665b15-a9ed-4abf-b9f5-cc27a668cf2a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left[ \frac{g}{3}\ \text{তে}\ \text{উপরে}\ \text{উঠলে},\ {g}^{{'}}=g+\frac{g}{3}=\frac{4g}{3}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e8665b15-a9ed-4abf-b9f5-cc27a668cf2a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e8665b15-a9ed-4abf-b9f5-cc27a668cf2a {text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001e8665b15-a9ed-4abf-b9f5-cc27a668cf2a {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
