                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000baf9bf14-8af2-4349-b53d-d3d9a1dd3972" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001baf9bf14-8af2-4349-b53d-d3d9a1dd3972"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," style="width: 1.423611in;height: 0.6483322in;" alt="C:\Users\Udvash\Desktop\Sinpping\27.JPG" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000baf9bf14-8af2-4349-b53d-d3d9a1dd3972 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001baf9bf14-8af2-4349-b53d-d3d9a1dd3972 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003bf27304-e255-4729-82f8-c1cadcbd7d22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left(40sin\ {30^{\circ} }\right)t+\frac{1}{2}g{t}^{2}=170⇒t=4.193\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013bf27304-e255-4729-82f8-c1cadcbd7d22"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003bf27304-e255-4729-82f8-c1cadcbd7d22 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013bf27304-e255-4729-82f8-c1cadcbd7d22 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000648c35ab-0d98-438b-9f6e-a4d587928f94" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=\left(40cos\ {30^{\circ} }\right)t\ m=40\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\times 4.193\ m=145.25\ m\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001648c35ab-0d98-438b-9f6e-a4d587928f94"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000648c35ab-0d98-438b-9f6e-a4d587928f94 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001648c35ab-0d98-438b-9f6e-a4d587928f94 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight