                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000006b87dc43-0837-448d-a577-5908ee207a08" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000016b87dc43-0837-448d-a577-5908ee207a08"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.8588714in;height: 0.746753in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006b87dc43-0837-448d-a577-5908ee207a08 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016b87dc43-0837-448d-a577-5908ee207a08 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000bf84c19c-e6a4-4884-bc61-a6acc1ce2b2b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(d=\frac{2}{3}\sqrt{{a}^{2}-{\left(\frac{a}{2}\right)}^{2}}=\frac{2}{3}.\ \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}a=\frac{a}{\sqrt{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001bf84c19c-e6a4-4884-bc61-a6acc1ce2b2b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000bf84c19c-e6a4-4884-bc61-a6acc1ce2b2b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001bf84c19c-e6a4-4884-bc61-a6acc1ce2b2b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000572b7535-5f22-4bc1-adbf-cf515ee7078a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(V=\frac{9\times {10}^{9}\times \sqrt{3}}{1\times {10}^{-3}}\left(3+2-1\right)=6.24\times {10}^{13}\ V\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001572b7535-5f22-4bc1-adbf-cf515ee7078a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000572b7535-5f22-4bc1-adbf-cf515ee7078a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001572b7535-5f22-4bc1-adbf-cf515ee7078a {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-s