                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000004e8954de-689c-473e-9db7-33ac9bdd0eca" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(x\right)=-5{x}^{2}+24x+4⇒{f}^{{'}}\left(x\right)=-10x+24=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014e8954de-689c-473e-9db7-33ac9bdd0eca"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004e8954de-689c-473e-9db7-33ac9bdd0eca {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014e8954de-689c-473e-9db7-33ac9bdd0eca {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c9207416-5ab9-48d6-8ae1-3b66031a192f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒x=+\frac{12}{5}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c9207416-5ab9-48d6-8ae1-3b66031a192f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c9207416-5ab9-48d6-8ae1-3b66031a192f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c9207416-5ab9-48d6-8ae1-3b66031a192f {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a497ed72-497e-420e-87fa-24407b9b152d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a497ed72-497e-420e-87fa-24407b9b152d"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a497ed72-497e-420e-87fa-24407b9b152d">&#184;i&#230;gvb </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=-5{\left(\frac{12}{5}\right)}^{2}+24⋅\frac{12}{5}+4=-\frac{144}{5}+\frac{288}{5}+4\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002a497ed72-497e-420e-87fa-24407