                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000009a560d19-caf2-4c0f-bf28-d07057526f9d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({10}^{2}={40}^{2}-2a\times \frac{450}{1000}⇒a=\frac{5000}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019a560d19-caf2-4c0f-bf28-d07057526f9d">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009a560d19-caf2-4c0f-bf28-d07057526f9d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019a560d19-caf2-4c0f-bf28-d07057526f9d {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000839babcc-2c17-40a5-b631-3b66730cd0ce" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(0={40}^{2}-2a\times S⇒S=\frac{{40}^{2}}{2a}=\frac{{40}^{2}}{2\times \frac{5000}{3}}=0.48=480\ m\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001839babcc-2c17-40a5-b631-3b66730cd0ce"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000839babcc-2c17-40a5-b631-3b66730cd0ce {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001839babcc-2c17-40a5-b631-3b66730cd0ce {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008a2c9b41-2b2b-4fe6-8ca7-c5adfb7f9bb3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018a2c9b41-2b2b-4fe6-8ca7-c5adfb7f9bb3"> </span><span class="pt-0000028a2c9b41-2b2b-4fe6-8ca7-c5adfb7f9bb3">AviI</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018a2c9b41-2b2b-4fe6-8ca7-c5adfb7f9bb3"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000028a2c9b41-2b2b-4fe6-8ca7-c5adfb7f9bb3">AwZ&#181;g Ki‡e </span><span class