                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000009f2eb1fe-733c-4064-8909-4dc615936007" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{a}{e}=9\sqrt{3};ae=3\sqrt{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019f2eb1fe-733c-4064-8909-4dc615936007"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009f2eb1fe-733c-4064-8909-4dc615936007 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019f2eb1fe-733c-4064-8909-4dc615936007 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002d78d4c1-8008-415f-b530-71bc33a29181" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{a}^{2}=27\times 3⇒a=9∴e=\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012d78d4c1-8008-415f-b530-71bc33a29181"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002d78d4c1-8008-415f-b530-71bc33a29181 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012d78d4c1-8008-415f-b530-71bc33a29181 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000044008ed5-43a7-441e-827b-833ae7564601" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(e=\sqrt{1-\frac{{b}^{2}}{{a}^{2}}}⇒\frac{1}{3}=1-\frac{{b}^{2}}{81}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000144008ed5-43a7-441e-827b-833ae7564601"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000044008ed5-43a7-441e-827b-833ae7564601 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000144008ed5-43a7-441e-827b-833ae7564601 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000d45b8fd6-b3f0-4e79-a87d-b8ca2f613b1d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{b}^{2}=81\left(1\frac{-1}{3}\right)=81\times \frac{2}{3}=54\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d45b8fd6-b3f0-4e79-a87d-b8ca2f613b1d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d45b8fd6-b3f0-4e79-a87d-b8ca2f613b1d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d45b8fd6-b3f0-4e79-a87d-b8ca2f613b1d {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒b=3\sqrt{6}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3"> †&#255;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=πab=27\sqrt{6}π\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3"> eM&#169; </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001fd0b3266-aec4-4257-a336-d2fca5e6a9e3 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
