                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000060135ca-d260-4b2c-accf-0e9634d5bbc6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}_{1}={e}^{ln⁡(lnx)}=lnx\ [∵\overset{}{\underset{a}{\begin{matrix}\\\end{matrix}}}{log}_{a}\ {b=b]\ }\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001060135ca-d260-4b2c-accf-0e9634d5bbc6"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000060135ca-d260-4b2c-accf-0e9634d5bbc6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001060135ca-d260-4b2c-accf-0e9634d5bbc6 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000656f2738-31bd-4cb8-9ee4-7cce3d9d489e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴y=\int lnx\ dx=xlnx-x+c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001656f2738-31bd-4cb8-9ee4-7cce3d9d489e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000656f2738-31bd-4cb8-9ee4-7cce3d9d489e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001656f2738-31bd-4cb8-9ee4-7cce3d9d489e {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000de9de5d6-677a-48d1-a752-de775f1baf15" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001de9de5d6-677a-48d1-a752-de775f1baf15">(e, 2)</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002de9de5d6-677a-48d1-a752-de775f1baf15"> we›`y‡Z, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(2\ =eln\ {e}-e+c\ ∴c=2\ \ \ ∴y=x\left(lnx-1\right)+2\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000de9de5d6-677a-48d1-a752-de775f1baf15 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}spa