                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000d077a341-0731-425c-a990-8133b0ed3e67" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d077a341-0731-425c-a990-8133b0ed3e67">†&#255;&#206;dj </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(={\int_{1}^{4} \sqrt{x}dx=\frac{2}{3}{\left[ {x}^{\frac{3}{2}}\right] }^{4}}_{1}=\frac{2}{3}\left(8-1\right)=\frac{14}{3}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d077a341-0731-425c-a990-8133b0ed3e67 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d077a341-0731-425c-a990-8133b0ed3e67 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
