                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000002a97a5a5-a539-49e5-9a26-7ee7236cd103" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(1,-1\right)={1}^{2}+{\left(-1\right)}^{2}+4-4+1=3≠0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012a97a5a5-a539-49e5-9a26-7ee7236cd103"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002a97a5a5-a539-49e5-9a26-7ee7236cd103 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012a97a5a5-a539-49e5-9a26-7ee7236cd103 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000f26eb55b-e460-4426-9cf2-39c982803ad6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span class="pt-000001f26eb55b-e460-4426-9cf2-39c982803ad6">e„‡&#203;i evB‡i Aew&#175;’Z|</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000f26eb55b-e460-4426-9cf2-39c982803ad6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001f26eb55b-e460-4426-9cf2-39c982803ad6 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000842233d4-9d7b-4524-83c1-36aaed056c9c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001842233d4-9d7b-4524-83c1-36aaed056c9c">awi, &#175;&#250;k&#169;K, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y+1=m\left(x-1\right)⇒y+1=mx-m\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000842233d4-9d7b-4524-83c1-36aaed056c9c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001842233d4-9d7b-4524-83c1-36aaed056c9c {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;