                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000009ed610e2-a1cd-482f-b8a1-f41826bbc25b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(cos\ {x}+2sin\ {x}=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019ed610e2-a1cd-482f-b8a1-f41826bbc25b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009ed610e2-a1cd-482f-b8a1-f41826bbc25b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019ed610e2-a1cd-482f-b8a1-f41826bbc25b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000031190834-cc7f-461c-a735-e89925318f77" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}cos\ {x}+\frac{2}{\sqrt{5}}sin\ {x}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}⇒cos\ {\left(x-α\right)}=cos\ {α}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000131190834-cc7f-461c-a735-e89925318f77"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000031190834-cc7f-461c-a735-e89925318f77 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000131190834-cc7f-461c-a735-e89925318f77 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005e455c06-5627-4adb-b020-62565e93a59d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒x-α=2nπ±α;\ α={cos}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015e455c06-5627-4adb-b020-62565e93a59d"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005e455c06-5627-4adb-b020-62565e93a59d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015e455c06-5627-4adb-b020-62565e93a59d {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: nor